        "title": {
          "english": "Being Polite: 'Please'",
          "arabic": "كن مؤدباً: 'من فضلك'"
        },
        "text": "To be polite when asking for information, use 'من فضلك' (min faḍlak) for a male or 'من فضلكِ' (min faḍlik) for a female, meaning 'please'.",
