        "title": {
          "english": "Asking for Address or Email",
          "arabic": "كيف تسأل عن العنوان أو الإيميل"
        },
        "text": "To ask for an address or email, you can use 'إيه؟' (ēh?), meaning 'what?'. For example, 'عنوانك إيه؟' (ʿunwānak ēh?) means 'What is your address?' (to a male). For a female, it's 'عنوانكِ إيه؟' (ʿunwānik ēh?). The same pattern applies to 'إيميلك إيه؟'.",
