        },
        "text": "To ask for a passport number, you'd say 'رقم باسبوركَ كام؟' (raqam basboorak kām?) for a male or 'رقم باسبورِك كام؟' (raqam basboorik kām?) for a female. Similarly for an ID card: 'رقم بطاقتكَ كام؟' (raqam baṭaʾtak kām?) for a male and 'رقم بطاقتِك كام؟' (raqam baṭaʾtik kām?) for a female.",
